Component based environment for gas turbine engine performance analysis.
Object-oriented architecture for steady and transient-state simulation of any GT configuration.
Evaluation of different off-design operation, but also for emission calculation and control system design.
It includes a 1-D combusor model with multiple thermo-chemical reactions.
